       "andom time variance in seconds added or subtracted from 'wait' delay ("
       "default 0 - see Notes)."$0D"'team' - Set this to team items. Teamed it"
       "ems will respawn randomly after team master is picked up (see Notes)."$0D
       "'target' - Picking up the item will trigger the entity this points to."
       $0D"'targetname' - A target_give entity can point to this for respawn f"
       "reebies."$0D"'notfree' - When set to 1, entity will not spawn in 'Free"
       " for all' and 'Tournament' modes."$0D"'notteam' - When set to 1, entit"
       "y will not spawn in 'Teamplay' and 'CTF' modes."$0D"'notsingle' - When"
       " set to 1, entity will not spawn in Single Player mode (bot play mode)"
       "."$0D"'notbot' - When set to 1, bots will not be able to see or use th"
       "is entity."$0D"==============NOTES==============================="$0D"T"
       "he amount of time it takes for an item in the team to respawn is deter"
       "mined by the 'wait' value of the item that was picked up previously. S"
       "o if one of the items in the team has it's 'wait' key set to -1 (never"
       " respawn), the random respawning cycle of the teamed items will stop a"
       "fter that item is picked up."$0D"When the random key is set, it's valu"
       "e is used to calculate a minimum and a maximum delay. The final time d"
       "elay will be a random value anywhere between the minimum and maximum v"
       "alues: (min delay = wait - random) (max delay = wait + random)."$0D"=="
       "===MODEL FOR MAPPING VISUAL ONLY================"$0D"Model not complet"
       "e enough to be worth the having."$0D"======DO NOT SET AS KEY OR VALUE="
       "================="
      bbox = '-16 -16 -16 16 16 16'
      spawnflags: =
      {
        txt = "&"
        typ = "X1"
        cap = "SUSPENDED"
      }
    }
    weapon_saber:form =
    {
      help = "===========DESCRIPTION============================"$0D"A Jedi Kn"
       "ight's weapon. If I have to break this down you're in trouble."$0D"==="
       "========SPAWNFLAGS============================="$0D"SUSPENDED - Item w"
       "ill spawn where it was placed in map and won't drop to the floor."$0D"="
       "==========KEYS&VALUES============================"$0D"'wait' - Time in"
       " seconds before item respawns after being picked up (default 5, -1 = n"
       "ever respawn)."$0D"'random' - Random time variance in seconds added or"
       " subtracted from 'wait' delay (default 0 - see Notes)."$0D"'team' - Se"
       "t this to team items. Teamed items will respawn randomly after team ma"
       "ster is picked up (see Notes)."$0D"'target' - Picking up the item will"
       " trigger the entity this points to."$0D"'targetname' - A target_give e"
