       "======================"$0D"SUSPENDED - Item will spawn where it was pl"
       "aced in map and won't drop to the floor."$0D"===========KEYS&VALUES==="
       "========================="$0D"'wait' - Time in seconds before item res"
       "pawns after being picked up (default 5, -1 = never respawn)."$0D"'rand"
       "om' - Random time variance in seconds added or subtracted from 'wait' "
       "delay (default 0 - see Notes)."$0D"'count' - Sets the amount of ammo g"
       "iven to the player when weapon is picked up (default 50)."$0D"'team' -"
       " Set this to team items. Teamed items will respawn randomly after team"
       " master is picked up (see Notes)."$0D"'target' - Picking up the item w"
       "ill trigger the entity this points to."$0D"'targetname' - A target_giv"
       "e entity can point to this for respawn freebies."$0D"'notfree' - When "
       "set to 1, entity will not spawn in 'Free for all' and 'Tournament' mod"
       "es."$0D"'notteam' - When set to 1, entity will not spawn in 'Teamplay'"
       " and 'CTF' modes."$0D"'notsingle' - When set to 1, entity will not spa"
       "wn in Single Player mode (bot play mode)."$0D"'notbot' - When set to 1"
       ", bots will not be able to see or use this entity."$0D"==============N"
       "OTES==============================="$0D"The amount of time it takes fo"
       "r an item in the team to respawn is determined by the 'wait' value of "
       "the item that was picked up previously. So if one of the items in the "
       "team has it's 'wait' key set to -1 (never respawn), the random respawn"
       "ing cycle of the teamed items will stop after that item is picked up."$0D
       "When the random key is set, it's value is used to calculate a minimum "
       "and a maximum delay. The final time delay will be a random value anywh"
       "ere between the minimum and maximum values: (min delay = wait - random"
       ") (max delay = wait + random)."$0D"=====MODEL FOR MAPPING VISUAL ONLY="
       "==============="$0D"Model not complete enough to be worth the having."$0D
       "======DO NOT SET AS KEY OR VALUE=================="
      bbox = '-16 -16 -16 16 16 16'
      spawnflags: =
      {
        txt = "&"
        typ = "X1"
        cap = "SUSPENDED"
      }
    }
