       "======================="$0D"'wait' - Time in seconds before item respa"
       "wns after being picked up (default 5, -1 = never respawn)."$0D"'random"
       "' - Random time variance in seconds added or subtracted from 'wait' de"
       "lay (default 0 - see Notes)."$0D"'count' - Sets the amount of ammo giv"
       "en to the player when weapon is picked up (default 3)."$0D"'team' - Se"
       "t this to team items. Teamed items will respawn randomly after team ma"
       "ster is picked up (see Notes)."$0D"'target' - Picking up the item will"
       " trigger the entity this points to."$0D"'targetname' - A target_give e"
       "ntity can point to this for respawn freebies."$0D"'notfree' - When set"
       " to 1, entity will not spawn in 'Free for all' and 'Tournament' modes."
       $0D"'notteam' - When set to 1, entity will not spawn in 'Teamplay' and "
       "'CTF' modes."$0D"'notsingle' - When set to 1, entity will not spawn in"
       " Single Player mode (bot play mode)."$0D"'notbot' - When set to 1, bot"
       "s will not be able to see or use this entity."$0D"==============NOTES="
       "=============================="$0D"The amount of time it takes for an "
       "item in the team to respawn is determined by the 'wait' value of the i"
       "tem that was picked up previously. So if one of the items in the team "
       "has it's 'wait' key set to -1 (never respawn), the random respawning c"
       "ycle of the teamed items will stop after that item is picked up."$0D"W"
       "hen the random key is set, it's value is used to calculate a minimum a"
       "nd a maximum delay. The final time delay will be a random value anywhe"
       "re between the minimum and maximum values: (min delay = wait - random)"
       " (max delay = wait + random)."$0D"=====MODEL FOR MAPPING VISUAL ONLY=="
       "=============="$0D"model="$22"models\weapons2\detpack\det_pack_pu.md3"$22
       $0D"======DO NOT SET AS KEY OR VALUE=================="
