       "=KEYS&VALUES============================"$0D"'target' - Targets will b"
       "e fired when someone spawns in on them."$0D"'nobots' - Will prevent bo"
       "ts from using this spot."$0D"'nohumans' - Will prevent non-bots from u"
       "sing this spot."$0D"'notfree' - When set to 1, entity will not spawn i"
       "n 'Free for all' and 'Tournament' modes."$0D"'notteam' - When set to 1"
       ", entity will not spawn in 'Teamplay' and 'CTF' modes."$0D"'notsingle'"
       " - When set to 1, entity will not spawn in Single Player mode (bot pla"
       "y mode)."$0D"'angle' - Direction in which player will look when spawni"
       "ng in the game. Does not apply to bots. 1 - 359 and -1 and -2 can be u"
       "sed for momentum purposes."$0D"==============NOTES===================="
       "==========="$0D"This can point at a target_give entity for respawn fre"
       "ebies."
      bbox = '-16 -16 -24 16 16 32'
