       " - Entities to use when this intermission point is chosen."$0D"======="
       "=======NOTES==============================="$0D"When time limit is rea"
       "ched you wait for game to end looking from here. This when used at the"
       " end of game (time limit) can cause things to happen. (Target2 key) In"
       " other words a scripted event or any entity could be used."
