       "spawned dies?)."$0D"'target2' - Fired by stasis spawners when they try"
       " to spawn while their spawner model is broken."$0D"'target3' - Fired b"
       "y spawner if they try to spawn and are blocked and have a wait < 0 (re"
       "moves them)."$0D"'count' - How many NPCs to spawn (only if targeted) d"
       "efault = 1."$0D"'wait' - If trying to spawn and blocked, how many seco"
       "nds to wait before trying again (default = 0.5, < 0 = never try again "
       "and fire target2)."$0D"'delay' - After spawned or triggered, how many "
       "seconds to wait to spawn the NPC."$0D"'showhealth' - Set to 1 to show "
       "health bar on this entity when crosshair is over it."$0D"'teamowner' -"
       " Crosshair shows green for this team, red for opposite team."$0D"0 - n"
       "one"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamuser' - Only this team can use t"
       "his NPC."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamnodmg' - Team "
       "that NPC does not take damage from (turrets and other auto-defenses th"
       "at have 'alliedTeam' set to this team won't target this NPC)."$0D"0 - "
