       "t loading and usage of basic sounds (pain, death, etc)."$0D"'noCombatS"
       "ounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of combat sounds (anger"
       ", victory, etc.)."$0D"'noExtraSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading an"
       "d usage of 'extra' sounds (chasing the enemy - detecting them, flankin"
