       "'health' - Starting health (default = 100)."$0D"======================"
       "============================"$0D"These are scripts that are called int"
       "o use under these circumstances."$0D"'spawnscript' - Default script to"
       " run once spawned (none by default)."$0D"'usescript' - Default script "
       "to run when used (none by default)."$0D"'awakescript' - Default script"
