       "ipt to run once angered (none by default)."$0D"'painscript' - Default "
       "script to run when hit (none by default)."$0D"'fleescript' - Default s"
       "cript to run when hit and below 50% health (none by default)."$0D"'dea"
       "thscript' - Default script to run when killed (none by default)."$0D"="
       "=============NOTES==============================="$0D"Has a red lights"
       "aber and force powers, uses her saber style from JK2"
