    NPC_Stormtrooper:form =
    {
      help = "===========DESCRIPTION============================"$0D"Spawns NP"
       "C Stormtrooper."$0D"===========SPAWNFLAGS============================="
       $0D"OFFICER - 60 health, flechette."$0D"COMMANDER - 60 health, heavy re"
       "peater."$0D"ALTOFFICER - 60 health, alt-fire flechette (grenades)."$0D
       "ROCKET - 60 health, rocket launcher."$0D"DROPTOFLOOR - NPC can be in a"
       "ir, but will spawn on the closest floor surface below it."$0D"CINEMATI"
       "C - Will spawn with no default AI (BS_CINEMATIC)."$0D"NOTSOLID - Start"
       "s not solid."$0D"STARTINSOLID - Don't try to fix if spawn in solid."$0D
       "SHY - Spawner is shy."$0D"===========KEYS&VALUES======================"
       "======"$0D"'targetname' - Name this NPC goes by for targeting."$0D"'ta"
       "rget' - NPC will fire this when it spawns it's last NPC (should this b"
       "e when the last NPC it spawned dies?)."$0D"'target2' - Fired by stasis"
       " spawners when they try to spawn while their spawner model is broken."$0D
       "'target3' - Fired by spawner if they try to spawn and are blocked and "
       "have a wait < 0 (removes them)."$0D"'count' - How many NPCs to spawn ("
       "only if targeted) default = 1."$0D"'wait' - If trying to spawn and blo"
       "cked, how many seconds to wait before trying again (default = 0.5, < 0"
       " = never try again and fire target2)."$0D"'delay' - After spawned or t"
       "riggered, how many seconds to wait to spawn the NPC."$0D"'showhealth' "
       "- Set to 1 to show health bar on this entity when crosshair is over it"
       "."$0D"'teamowner' - Crosshair shows green for this team, red for oppos"
       "ite team."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamuser' - Only "
       "this team can use this NPC."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'"
       "teamnodmg' - Team that NPC does not take damage from (turrets and othe"
       "r auto-defenses that have 'alliedTeam' set to this team won't target t"
       "his NPC)."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'noBasicSounds' - "
       "Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of basic sounds (pain, death, et"
       "c)."$0D"'noCombatSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of co"
       "mbat sounds (anger, victory, etc.)."$0D"'noExtraSounds' - Set to 1 to "
       "prevent loading and usage of 'extra' sounds (chasing the enemy - detec"
       "ting them, flanking them... also Jedi combat sounds)."$0D"'NPC_targetn"
       "ame' - NPC's targetname AND script_targetname."$0D"'NPC_target' - NPC'"
       "s target to fire when killed."$0D"'NPC_target2' - NPC's target to fire"
