    NPC_Snowtrooper:form =
    {
      help = "===========DESCRIPTION============================"$0D"Spawns NP"
       "C Snowtrooper."$0D"===========SPAWNFLAGS============================="$0D
       "DROPTOFLOOR - NPC can be in air, but will spawn on the closest floor s"
       "urface below it."$0D"CINEMATIC - Will spawn with no default AI (BS_CIN"
       "EMATIC)."$0D"NOTSOLID - Starts not solid."$0D"STARTINSOLID - Don't try"
       " to fix if spawn in solid."$0D"SHY - Spawner is shy."$0D"===========KE"
       "YS&VALUES============================"$0D"'targetname' - Name this NPC"
       " goes by for targeting."$0D"'target' - NPC will fire this when it spaw"
       "ns it's last NPC (should this be when the last NPC it spawned dies?)."$0D
       "'target2' - Fired by stasis spawners when they try to spawn while thei"
       "r spawner model is broken."$0D"'target3' - Fired by spawner if they tr"
       "y to spawn and are blocked and have a wait < 0 (removes them)."$0D"'co"
       "unt' - How many NPCs to spawn (only if targeted) default = 1."$0D"'wai"
       "t' - If trying to spawn and blocked, how many seconds to wait before t"
       "rying again (default = 0.5, < 0 = never try again and fire target2)."$0D
       "'delay' - After spawned or triggered, how many seconds to wait to spaw"
       "n the NPC."$0D"'showhealth' - Set to 1 to show health bar on this enti"
       "ty when crosshair is over it."$0D"'teamowner' - Crosshair shows green "
       "for this team, red for opposite team."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 -"
       " blue"$0D"'teamuser' - Only this team can use this NPC."$0D"0 - none"$0D
       "1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamnodmg' - Team that NPC does not take dam"
       "age from (turrets and other auto-defenses that have 'alliedTeam' set t"
       "o this team won't target this NPC)."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - b"
       "lue"$0D"'noBasicSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of bas"
       "ic sounds (pain, death, etc)."$0D"'noCombatSounds' - Set to 1 to preve"
       "nt loading and usage of combat sounds (anger, victory, etc.)."$0D"'noE"
       "xtraSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of 'extra' sounds "
       "(chasing the enemy - detecting them, flanking them... also Jedi combat"
       " sounds)."$0D"'NPC_targetname' - NPC's targetname AND script_targetnam"
       "e."$0D"'NPC_target' - NPC's target to fire when killed."$0D"'NPC_targe"
       "t2' - NPC's target to fire when knocked out."$0D"'NPC_target4' - NPC's"
       " target to fire when killed by friendly fire."$0D"'health' - Starting "
       "health (default = 100)."$0D"=========================================="
       "========"$0D"These are scripts that are called into use under these ci"
       "rcumstances."$0D"'spawnscript' - Default script to run once spawned (n"
