       " best lightsaber fighter and uses no force powers.  Red saber, 100 hea"
       "lth."$0D"BOSS - Quite acrobatic, good lightsaber fighter and uses forc"
       "e powers.  Orange saber, 150 health."$0D"CEILING - Sticks to the ceili"
       "ng until he sees an enemy or takes pain."$0D"CINEMATIC - Will spawn wi"
       "th no default AI (BS_CINEMATIC)."$0D"NOTSOLID - Starts not solid."$0D"S"
       "TARTINSOLID - Don't try to fix if spawn in solid."$0D"SHY - Spawner is"
       " shy."$0D"===========KEYS&VALUES============================"$0D"'targ"
       "etname' - Name this NPC goes by for targeting."$0D"'target' - NPC will"
       " fire this when it spawns it's last NPC (should this be when the last "
       "NPC it spawned dies?)."$0D"'target2' - Fired by stasis spawners when t"
       "hey try to spawn while their spawner model is broken."$0D"'target3' - "
       "Fired by spawner if they try to spawn and are blocked and have a wait "
       "< 0 (removes them)."$0D"'count' - How many NPCs to spawn (only if targ"
       "eted) default = 1."$0D"'wait' - If trying to spawn and blocked, how ma"
       "ny seconds to wait before trying again (default = 0.5, < 0 = never try"
       " again and fire target2)."$0D"'delay' - After spawned or triggered, ho"
       "w many seconds to wait to spawn the NPC."$0D"'showhealth' - Set to 1 t"
       "o show health bar on this entity when crosshair is over it."$0D"'teamo"
       "wner' - Crosshair shows green for this team, red for opposite team."$0D
       "0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamuser' - Only this team can "
       "use this NPC."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamnodmg' - "
       "Team that NPC does not take damage from (turrets and other auto-defens"
