       "argetname AND script_targetname."$0D"'NPC_target' - NPC's target to fi"
       "re when killed."$0D"'NPC_target2' - NPC's target to fire when knocked "
       "out."$0D"'NPC_target4' - NPC's target to fire when killed by friendly "
       "fire."$0D"'health' - Starting health (default = 100)."$0D"============"
       "======================================"$0D"These are scripts that are "
       "called into use under these circumstances."$0D"'spawnscript' - Default"
       " script to run once spawned (none by default)."$0D"'usescript' - Defau"
       "lt script to run when used (none by default)."$0D"'awakescript' - Defa"
       "ult script to run once awoken (none by default)."$0D"'angerscript' - D"
