       "is NPC goes by for targeting."$0D"'target' - NPC will fire this when i"
       "t spawns it's last NPC (should this be when the last NPC it spawned di"
       "es?)."$0D"'target2' - Fired by stasis spawners when they try to spawn "
       "while their spawner model is broken."$0D"'target3' - Fired by spawner "
       "if they try to spawn and are blocked and have a wait < 0 (removes them"
       ")."$0D"'count' - How many NPCs to spawn (only if targeted) default = 1"
       "."$0D"'wait' - If trying to spawn and blocked, how many seconds to wai"
       "t before trying again (default = 0.5, < 0 = never try again and fire t"
       "arget2)."$0D"'delay' - After spawned or triggered, how many seconds to"
       " wait to spawn the NPC."$0D"'showhealth' - Set to 1 to show health bar"
       " on this entity when crosshair is over it."$0D"'teamowner' - Crosshair"
       " shows green for this team, red for opposite team."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 "
       "- red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamuser' - Only this team can use this NPC."$0D
       "0 - none"$0D"1 - red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'teamnodmg' - Team that NPC does"
       " not take damage from (turrets and other auto-defenses that have 'alli"
       "edTeam' set to this team won't target this NPC)."$0D"0 - none"$0D"1 - "
       "red"$0D"2 - blue"$0D"'noBasicSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and"
       " usage of basic sounds (pain, death, etc)."$0D"'noCombatSounds' - Set "
       "to 1 to prevent loading and usage of combat sounds (anger, victory, et"
       "c.)."$0D"'noExtraSounds' - Set to 1 to prevent loading and usage of 'e"
       "xtra' sounds (chasing the enemy - detecting them, flanking them... als"
       "o Jedi combat sounds)."$0D"'NPC_targetname' - NPC's targetname AND scr"
       "ipt_targetname."$0D"'NPC_target' - NPC's target to fire when killed."$0D
       "'NPC_target2' - NPC's target to fire when knocked out."$0D"'NPC_target"
       "4' - NPC's target to fire when killed by friendly fire."$0D"'health' -"
       " Starting health (default = 100)."$0D"================================"
       "=================="$0D"These are scripts that are called into use unde"
       "r these circumstances."$0D"'spawnscript' - Default script to run once "
       "spawned (none by default)."$0D"'usescript' - Default script to run whe"
