       "ce awoken (none by default)."$0D"'angerscript' - Default script to run"
       " once angered (none by default)."$0D"'painscript' - Default script to "
       "run when hit (none by default)."$0D"'fleescript' - Default script to r"
       "un when hit and below 50% health (none by default)."$0D"'deathscript' "
       "- Default script to run when killed (none by default)."
