       "PTOFLOOR - NPC can be in air, but will spawn on the closest floor surf"
       "ace below it."$0D"CINEMATIC - Will spawn with no default AI (BS_CINEMA"
       "TIC)."$0D"NOTSOLID - Starts not solid."$0D"STARTINSOLID - Don't try to"
