      help = "===========DESCRIPTION============================"$0D"Spawns NP"
       "C Protocol Droid, also C3PO"$0D"===========SPAWNFLAGS================="
       "============"$0D"IMPERIAL - Spawns the Imperial version."$0D"DROPTOFLO"
       "OR - NPC can be in air, but will spawn on the closest floor surface be"
       "low it."$0D"CINEMATIC - Will spawn with no default AI (BS_CINEMATIC)."$0D
       "NOTSOLID - Starts not solid."$0D"STARTINSOLID - Don't try to fix if sp"
       "awn in solid."$0D"SHY - Spawner is shy."$0D"==============NOTES======="
